  "Description": {
    "English": "Equip this exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Personal Flair</span> in commemoration of the 'Beachhead' <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>, and your success in tracking the <span class=\"name name-special\">renegade historical echo</span>.<br><br>Apply this banner to your profile at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "装备上这枚专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">个人旗帜</span>，纪念你完成了“抢滩”<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>，并成功追踪了<span class=\"name name-special\">反叛者历史回音</span>。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>中将这面旗帜应用至你的个人档案。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "裝備這款獨家的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">個人造型</span>紀念「灘頭」<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>，及您在追蹤<span class=\"name name-special\">叛離者歷史回音</span>的成就。<br><br>能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>套用此旗幟到你的檔案。"
  },
